het said, \"Whoever obeys me enters Paradise, and whoever disobeys me has refused.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/five-pillars-and-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":24280,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Perform the five pillars, be kind to family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cTell me what I can do to enter Paradise and avoid Hellfire.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWorship Allah and do not associate anything with Him, perform the prayer, give in charity, and keep\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18089,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/09\/three-not-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24280,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Three people will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree persons will not be looked upon by Allah Almighty on the Day of Resurrection: one who disobeys his parents, a woman who imitates men, and a man who allows his women to fornicate. Three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u